From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 06:42:24 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Rename product XDG paths to astrohacker/termsurf

Config, data, state, and cache defaults now use the
termsurf product segment instead of terminal.
